Body:
t = Template(
    """
        <%def name="a()">
            this is a ${b()}
            <%def name="b()">
                this is b
                ${c()}
            </%def>

            <%def name="c()">
                this is c
            </%def>
        </%def>
        ${a()}
"""
    )
eq_(flatten_result(t.render()), 'this is a this is b this is c')
